smiles.info: Canonical SMILES string generated using RDKit

fields.j_values: str (coupling constants in Hz, separated by '_')

h_nmr_peaks.info: Array of peak information from 1H NMR spectrum automatically extracted

c_nmr_peaks.info: Array of peak information from 13C NMR spectrum automatically extracted

hsqc_nmr_spectrum.info: 2D HSQC NMR spectrum intensity matrix. Use np.stack to make a 2D array out of it

hsqc_nmr_peaks.info: Array of correlation peaks from HSQC spectrum

ir_spectra.info: IR absorption spectrum intensity values, from 400cm^{-1} to 4000cm^{-1} using 1800points

msms_cfmid_positive_10ev.info: MS/MS spectrum at 10eV collision energy in positive ion mode

msms_cfmid_positive_40ev.info: MS/MS spectrum at 40eV collision energy in positive ion mode

msms_cfmid_fragments_positive.info: Predicted fragments with SMILES/molecular formulas in positive ion mode

msms_cfmid_negative_10ev.info: MS/MS spectrum at 10eV collision energy in negative ion mode

msms_cfmid_negative_20ev.info: MS/MS spectrum at 20eV collision energy in negative ion mode

msms_cfmid_negative_40ev.info: MS/MS spectrum at 40eV collision energy in negative ion mode

msms_cfmid_fragments_negative.info: Predicted fragments with SMILES/molecular formulas in negative ion mode

msms_iceberg_positive.info: MS/MS spectrum with normalized intensities using ICEBERG (positive ion mode)
